      "content": "interesting. so if the \"social fabric\" is the issue, are u saying that certain racial or cultural backgrounds are inherently more likely to cause this kind of instability or friction in a real estate context? like, does the specific demographic makeup of the new population change the risk profile compared to, say, just an influx of young professionals?",
